parameters: Karen: "So... is this equation correct here, I wonder?"
Ginga: "Ah, as expected of Saionji-san. You catch on quickly."
Karen: "Maybe my mind is clearer because Amasawa-kun is beside me."
Ginga: "Oh, the answer for the next problem is wrong."
Ginga: "Look, there's a mistake in the final multiplication."
Karen: "If this goes like this... and with this, it's good!"
Ginga: "I can't do much else, but I'm glad you're pleased."

Karen: "Samejima's place is on the fifth floor of a mansion called
\C[17]Sky High\C[0] in the \C[17]Fols district's pleasure
quarter\C[0]."

Karen: "It's just a rumor that he was seen with someone there, so he
might not be there."
Karen: "If he says he wants it, I'll give him anything."

Karen: "Sneaky maneuvers... a liar, a coward. But he's a man who
delivers results."
Karen: "Indeed, Amasawa is acting just as he said."

Karen: "When it comes to love matters, he's unbelievably quick-
witted."

Karen: "Only someone like him could seduce Morisaki from that
situation."
Karen: "Amasawa, I will make you taste the same suffering as me."
